Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.69,0:02:33.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你不仅仅活了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还肩负起了我国的指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太可靠了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.35,0:02:42.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以你为荣 亚瑟拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.17,0:02:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.00,0:02:48.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许是我的心理作用 你好像变得坚强了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为发生了很多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.16,0:02:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们往往会在经验中发生改变吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.97,0:03:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲜红的大地 保佑你武运昌隆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:06.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你完全没变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.42,0:03:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼叫三叉戟基地 我是Deucalion的马格巴丽吉舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.25,0:03:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请求入港
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.56,0:03:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎您的到来 Deucalion
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,批准你们的入港
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.41,0:03:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请停泊到12号码头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Deucalion了解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.15,0:03:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路线设为三叉戟基地对接舱 在12号码头进行停泊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.15,0:03:32.96,ruby,NTP,0,45,0,,docking bay
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始减速
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始减速
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.20,0:03:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是利用火星的技术建造出来的战舰吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说预备役前的小孩子们也在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:50.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好庞大的战力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.95,0:03:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们一定将能召集到的部队都召集到这里了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.94,0:03:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这是一次大规模作战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:04:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离减速完成还有5秒…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.58,0:04:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3 2 1！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.77,0:04:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两舷停止 已相对停止于12号码头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全舰停止 系泊完成后立刻进行检查和补给
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.67,0:04:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,界冢少尉 你在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,门开着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,状态如何 伊奈帆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.18,0:04:37.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不错 虽然还有点疼就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,药呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.57,0:04:40.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然吃了药会感觉好一些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但吃药了会使神经链路的敏感度下降
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也挺不容易的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去和普通的眼睛没啥区别呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西很厉害吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.72,0:05:00.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勉勉强强凑合着用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是开发中的原型样板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还得进一步改良程序
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过大多数东西都是可以辨认出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.88,0:05:08.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,体重 49.2公斤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.22,0:05:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你长胖了点？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你为什么会知道啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:23.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用三维测量计算了在你接住200g包裹时的动量变化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从而计算出了你的总重量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此基础上减去了制服的重量就得出结果了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家才没有胖啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.17,0:05:32.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家只不过经过锻炼长肌肉了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.03,0:05:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是在说谎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:37.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过对你声音的共振峰分析能看出你很紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:37.19,ruby,NTP,0,100,0,,formant
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:39.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那东西不是坏了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.55,0:05:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常正常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.25,0:05:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.12,0:05:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也能从她的声音里听出同样的紧张感
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.71,0:05:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.30,0:05:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}我是巴斯帝国第一皇女 亚瑟拉姆·巴斯·艾莉欧西亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这台词是骗人的…那么这就意味着…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.14,0:05:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不是真正的公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:06:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然刚刚的波形是说谎了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,压力太大吃多了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃你妹！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧张度又上升了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也不和你说话了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.73,0:06:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:16.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.92,0:06:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是觉得韵子太容易读懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.39,0:06:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.94,0:06:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你其实是个笨蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.71,0:06:33.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有说谎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.95,0:06:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯雷因大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.58,0:06:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾德尔丽泽 你不用伺候雷姆蕾娜公主吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.23,0:06:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 我会替你保密的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.94,0:06:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.84,0:06:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 我找到了你之前跟我说的那艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.51,0:06:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是Deucalion吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那艘船好像暗中经过修理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.72,0:07:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说他们打倒雅克伊姆男爵后飞到宇宙来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.00,0:07:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有可能要跟他们战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.72,0:07:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟拉姆公主会伤心的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下何时会醒过来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.84,0:07:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果她就这样一直不…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.48,0:07:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一定会再次看到她的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.86,0:07:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.58,0:07:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.12,0:07:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟拉姆就托付给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都已经安排好了 请您放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.87,0:08:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到之前谎称她已经被暗杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.65,0:08:13.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次却要谎称她还活着…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯雷因啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.38,0:08:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么看待现在的巴斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.61,0:08:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这种人怎敢对神圣的大地抱有意见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓 尽管说出你的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.24,0:08:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有力量的市民为生活所困扰的社会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为通过攻击地球 将之纳入我国版图 获取资源
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.62,0:08:37.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以得到财富
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.17,0:08:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些财富很可能会流向上层阶级
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不会改善市民的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你要怎么去做？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aldnoah…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.17,0:08:56.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得Aldnoah者掌控一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:09:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是一切问题的根源
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.44,0:09:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发掘出Aldnoah确实是皇帝陛下的丰功伟绩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.57,0:09:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他将此力量独占
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.92,0:09:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并建立起由有力量的人支配的社会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.37,0:09:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,则是一个很大的罪过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.73,0:09:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在赢得战争 支配地球之时
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将改变那颗鲜红的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为我贡献你的力量 斯雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 扎赫巴姆伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.12,0:09:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的爱骑准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.02,0:09:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,启动测试已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后只要完成各单元的同步调整就可以实战了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.12,0:09:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在岛上进行调整
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.05,0:09:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stygis队 准备出击！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.14,0:09:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.25,0:09:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tharsis 启动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.10,0:09:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有启动？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aldnoah Drive停止了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.79,0:10:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷姆蕾娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.49,0:10:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什么事了吗 斯雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.67,0:10:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您为什么要停止Tharsis呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:26.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:31.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里只有公主殿下可以强制停止Aldnoah
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.66,0:10:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.98,0:10:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请启动Aldnoah
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.30,0:10:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.29,0:10:44.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去拜托皇姐如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.96,0:10:47.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前我就觉得很不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.02,0:10:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底你一个地球人 为何能驱动Tharsis
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来皇姐也相当幸福呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.62,0:10:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都变成这副惨样了还有人深爱着她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.71,0:11:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明父亲都是同一个人 仅仅因为母亲有别
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就没任何人来理会我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.63,0:11:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都很仰慕雷姆蕾娜公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:12.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有骗您
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是在骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们所仰慕的不是我 而是我的启动因子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.21,0:11:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你才来到这里的不是么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.44,0:11:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯雷因大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么想要我的帮助？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aldnoah对你就如此重要？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.79,0:11:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是皇姐的代替品？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.89,0:11:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…果然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.52,0:11:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.86,0:11:53.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出生于地球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.66,0:11:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当身为科学家的父亲去世后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去了依靠的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.99,0:12:00.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为了巴斯轨道骑士的仆人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会说我完全理解公主殿下您的艰辛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.82,0:12:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…我也是因出身而受苦之人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以您的苦恼 我想我还是理解一些的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我由衷仰慕你 我主雷姆蕾娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.48,0:12:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抬起头来 斯雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.77,0:12:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就能启动一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:43.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.33,0:12:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.71,0:12:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝您好运 斯雷因·托罗亚特骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯雷因大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:12:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很佩服你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.36,0:13:03.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能为您效劳 我非常光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.73,0:13:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见笑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.41,0:13:11.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全机发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标 马里内罗岛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:14.09,ruby,NTP,75,0,0,,Marineros
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.47,0:13:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所拥有的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:30.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都由我来继承吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.42,0:13:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 您就放心吧 皇姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.95,0:13:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们即将进入地球自转轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用航空制动 之后上升脱离 最后突入卫星带
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后前往马里内罗岛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯雷因大人 差不多是时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.78,0:14:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.89,0:14:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漂浮在卫星带里的无数的岩石
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.83,0:14:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正以地球为中心作椭圆轨道运动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.04,0:14:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们三叉戟基地也是那些岩石中的一个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.73,0:14:57.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而火星军的前线基地马里内罗轨道便是这条
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:15:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两者在72小时后到达最近点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.64,0:15:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其距离只有短短的7公里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:05.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是敌我双方可以肉眼目视彼此的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.75,0:15:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从而推测两基地间可能会因此发生大规模的攻防战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.90,0:15:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对此 我让轨道上以及地面上拥有强大战力的诸位集结到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.51,0:15:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们认为火星军也将聚集他们的全部力量发起总攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.89,0:15:23.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在座的各位请不要掉以轻心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.54,0:15:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来我进行作战说明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.80,0:15:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从开战以来 我们从来就没有打过如此大规模的宇宙战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:38.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是只要想想敌人也是第一次就没什么可怕的了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.74,0:15:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…我仍然感到不安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.49,0:15:48.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你这可爱的一面也在日常中展现的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该会多一点桃花运吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:53.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离减速结束还有5秒…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.59,0:15:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.98,0:15:59.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脱离
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺手给敌人一点见面礼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.52,0:16:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stygis队啊 为我展示你们的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.91,0:16:14.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stygis-1 谨遵上令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stygis-2 谨遵上令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stygis-3 谨遵上令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高热源体正从近地轨道方向急速接近这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.33,0:16:48.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌我识别信号没有应答
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.78,0:16:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然从下面来？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.08,0:16:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方正高速通过距离本基地2km的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取的是前往火星军马里内罗基地的轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令部发来了迎击命令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.90,0:17:03.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高速接近的中型船只7艘 以及3个小型机机影
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.81,0:17:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们打算在总攻开始之前发动突袭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可行动的全部舰载机出击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本舰也做好紧急发射的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.23,0:17:13.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.87,0:17:15.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的机体如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.04,0:17:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经完成了修理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.37,0:17:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙装备也更换好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:20.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.82,0:17:23.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过真要用这么显眼的颜色吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是发话 我就帮你换个色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 这算是一个标志
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.17,0:17:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ghanaati小队 配置结束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.46,0:17:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Harroway小队 配置结束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:52.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mustang-11 配置结束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.33,0:17:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mustang-22 配置结束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.92,0:17:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与敌机的相对速度为每秒3公里左右
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会在一瞬间擦肩而过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.61,0:18:02.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这意味着攻击的时机仅有一瞬间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.10,0:18:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stygis-1 开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.92,0:18:14.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stygis-2 开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.69,0:18:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stygis-3 开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.22,0:18:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方开始攻击了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:28.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风向太过复杂了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.94,0:18:44.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌我双方以目前这个距离都很难打中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.93,0:18:51.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打中了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.89,0:18:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个距离？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.49,0:18:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mustang-00 开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.33,0:18:59.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊奈帆！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.85,0:19:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高密度卫星群所产生的重力梯度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数据补正完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.19,0:19:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标设定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.67,0:19:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.31,0:19:12.01,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Got over it ages ago
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.31,0:19:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.68,0:19:15.71,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Where we were from the same river
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.18,0:19:19.57,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Thinking about how we lost our minds
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stygis队被…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:22.82,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I don't care what's in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.37,0:19:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊奈帆！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:26.98,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}They don't care about old trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.80,0:19:30.60,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Many wars wherever you go
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.19,0:19:32.44,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Somebody please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.55,0:19:34.50,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Can we stop all the fights?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.72,0:19:37.40,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I'll do it because it's my turn
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.81,0:19:36.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.46,0:19:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己来当诱饵来吸引对方的火力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:41.37,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}But don't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈库莱特先生 请采取回避运动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:45.51,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}There are people crying everyday
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.06,0:19:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.56,0:19:47.56,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Let's fly away
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:51.52,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}For Earth and Mars today!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.57,0:19:53.50,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Don't stop me now
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被打中！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.59,0:19:56.36,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Look around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.09,0:19:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲开了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.54,0:19:59.90,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}How can we stop the war
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.97,0:20:04.22,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Hello, But Are we sure enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.29,0:20:06.40,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}You'll come back tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.44,0:20:08.50,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}But I need to know that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.29,0:20:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很敏捷的动作…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:11.30,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Look around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:11.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正确无比的射击！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:14.70,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}So What are we fighting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:13.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然能这种乱风中打中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.72,0:20:16.64,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Can I ask you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:19.07,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Why the sky is blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:20.56,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}There's no difference
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:20.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速度？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.58,0:20:22.70,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}You and me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:22.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.06,0:20:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方看清了子弹的轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.41,0:20:26.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.34,0:20:27.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是怎样的敌人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:30.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.70,0:20:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,橙色的机体…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.81,0:20:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找你好久了 蝙蝠…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 现在变成海鸥了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:42.12,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Don't stop me now
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.20,0:20:45.18,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Look around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.37,0:20:48.63,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}How can we stop the war
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:52.96,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Hello, But Are we sure enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌舰团即将进入有效射程
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.04,0:20:55.27,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}You'll come back tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.43,0:20:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自由攻击！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.33,0:20:57.26,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}But I need to know that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.29,0:21:00.01,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Look around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.23,0:21:03.42,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}So What are we fighting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:05.32,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Can I ask you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.77,0:21:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊奈帆！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.84,0:21:07.61,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Why the sky is blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.81,0:21:09.36,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}There's no difference
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.39,0:21:11.49,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}You and me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.94,0:21:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌舰团通过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.36,0:21:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正驶离本区域
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.67,0:21:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续射击 直到敌人超出射程
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.40,0:21:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报告受损情况！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.91,0:21:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tharsis…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.49,0:21:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本是轨道骑士库鲁迪欧伯爵所有的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.87,0:21:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后为扎赫巴姆伯爵所有并配给了其麾下的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.18,0:21:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搭乘者的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.49,0:21:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,橙色的机体…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.37,0:21:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是练习机
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.08,0:21:47.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,练习机？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.21,0:21:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人就爱开练习机
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.84,0:21:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.85,0:21:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…他的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.39,0:21:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,界冢伊奈帆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.29,0:22:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.86,0:22:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.64,0:22:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯雷因·托罗亚特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.75,0:22:10.75,title,NTP,0,0,0,,“异星的邻人”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.29,0:22:32.62,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}在彷徨的未来 在狭隘的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.29,0:22:32.62,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}僕たちは彷徨える未来　窮屈な空に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.66,0:22:36.94,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我们探寻光明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.66,0:22:36.94,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}光を探している
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.52,0:22:40.98,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}震える手は無力で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.52,0:22:40.98,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}颤抖着的双手是无力的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.04,0:22:44.39,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}叫びはまた遠くて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.04,0:22:44.39,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}呐喊又在消失在远方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.45,0:22:52.80,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}だけど飛ぶこころ　恐れではいられない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.45,0:22:52.80,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}然而飞翔的心 不允许一丝的恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.67,0:23:00.81,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}永遠じゃなくでも　完璧じゃなくでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.67,0:23:00.81,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不永恒又何妨 不完美又何妨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.86,0:23:08.22,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}背中合わせの世界を真っ直ぐ生きていく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.86,0:23:08.22,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}只要在相互扶持的世界勇敢生存
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.31,0:23:15.40,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}何度傷ついでも　何度間違えでも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.31,0:23:15.40,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}一次次的受伤算什么 一次次的错误算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.52,0:23:21.06,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}運命さえ飛び越えて行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.52,0:23:21.06,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}即使是命运 我们也要一起飞越
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.14,0:23:24.72,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}この空の果てまで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.14,0:23:24.72,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}飞向天空的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.77,0:23:30.81,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}始まりを信じで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.77,0:23:30.81,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}相信着希望的开始

